      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Management Policy              : Strategic management challenges in developing and emerging economies. Focus on strategies that foster both firm competitiveness and economic development, including: technological capabilities, new forms of organization, small and large firms, global production, social impact, global standards and governance.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

